 * - CLEANUP_TARGET_DIR: Directory to clean (default: ~/code)
 * - CLEANUP_DRY_RUN: Dry run mode (default: false)
 * - RUN_ON_STARTUP: Controlled via config.runOnStartup (opt-in) or --run-now/--run CLI flags
